text: Saar Seys (born 26 July 1991) is a Belgian korfball player. She is a member of Floriant and the Belgium national korfball team. With the national team she won the silver medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==Achievements== ===Club=== *Topkorfbal League champion (indoor), 1x (2022) *Topkorfbal League champion (outdoor), 1x (2022) *Best player of the national league (2020) *, 1x (2019) ===National team=== ; World Games : 2017 World Games : 2022 World Games ; IKF World Korfball Championship : 2019 IKF World Korfball Championship ; European Korfball Championship : 4th 2018 IKF European Korfball A-Championship : 2021 IKF European Korfball A-Championship ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian korfball players Category:Sportswomen
title: Saar Seys
